{"id": 2358, "genre": 1001, "title": "【好奇心x帝舵】“天生敢为”，你如今最想挑战自己的一件事是什么？", "description": "突破自我的临门一脚，还是需要自己来踢！", "record_count": 10284, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180518200504oKhZ7ejUiATVu5ml.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 3, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-05-21T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 282880, "content": "减肥成功，保持体重??", "image": null, "praise_count": 80, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1107203}, {"id": 283136, "content": "挣多点钱，重新吃药，直到彻底治好抑郁和焦虑症。我想找回无穷无尽的快乐和思维敏捷的大脑。", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1349590}, {"id": 282882, "content": "挑战各种运动和习惯", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 505814}, {"id": 283138, "content": "不顾一切，来一场说走就走的世界旅行。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1303803}, {"id": 282883, "content": "不用在乎外界的说法，用自己的想法快乐地完成一切你想完成的事", "image": null, "praise_count": 369, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1350631}, {"id": 289027, "content": "拾起勇气  面对嘲笑与反对", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1363851}, {"id": 282884, "content": "看书考编\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1116241}, {"id": 282885, "content": "自己开车上高速…", "image": null, "praise_count": 45, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1207126}, {"id": 282886, "content": "临睡觉前 看半个小时书", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1344200}, {"id": 285958, "content": "踢球", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1366390}, {"id": 282888, "content": "当了多年全职妈妈，现在想重返职场", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1225746}, {"id": 283144, "content": "jjjj", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1351680}, {"id": 283912, "content": "做一件一辈子都让自己看得起的事情！比如：参军？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 871583}, {"id": 284936, "content": "为员工提供每年至少两个月的带薪年假", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1345326}, {"id": 282889, "content": "放弃教师公务员“都是为你好”的铁饭碗，做一个父母长辈眼中的“无业游民”，为我真正想做的事真的去努力一把，哪怕头破血流。", "image": null, "praise_count": 280, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1350647}, {"id": 283145, "content": "我要上弹幕", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1351680}, {"id": 282890, "content": "对“临门一脚”还是要自己来踢，这句话特别认同！天生敢为，就是要把主动权掌握在自己手里！Go Go Go", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 602753}, {"id": 282891, "content": "能够在做任何事情的时候保持专注", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1350656}, {"id": 283147, "content": "看不到自己发的弹幕", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1351680}, {"id": 282892, "content": "哈哈，蹦极", "image": null, "praise_count": 67, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1345924}, {"id": 282893, "content": "每天看手机不超过2小时，早睡早起", "image": null, "praise_count": 71, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1322053}, {"id": 282894, "content": "不接受自己是个平凡人，并尝试改变", "image": null, "praise_count": 41, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1124700}, {"id": 282895, "content": "换一个职业", "image": null, "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1347848}, {"id": 282896, "content": "裸辞休息两个月，整理好自己再重新出发。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 599749}, {"id": 282897, "content": "做真实的自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 970428}, {"id": 282898, "content": "可以到级部前一百 考上上海财经", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1318920}, {"id": 283922, "content": "深潜", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1333885}, {"id": 282899, "content": "辞掉工作，没有存款和收入，去学习一项你并不擅长的新领域，前途未卜，家庭孩子还在担上。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1340863}, {"id": 282900, "content": "找女朋友", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1003063}, {"id": 283924, "content": "不按照既定的安逸或者平庸的方式生活，无所顾忌的拼一把", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1347401}, {"id": 282901, "content": "一切胆怯的事", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 851806}, {"id": 282903, "content": "辞掉工作，第三次考研究生。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1350682}, {"id": 282904, "content": "极少真正出门500米\n我想像《白日梦想家》一样", "image": "img/option/option/2018052112283675OntohvgTeya3Nu.jpg", "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1349838}, {"id": 282905, "content": "每周一本书，戒掉拖延症，改变自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1350689}, {"id": 282906, "content": "一天花掉100万", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 782034}, {"id": 285210, "content": "吃屎", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1362231}, {"id": 282907, "content": "不读书，不创业，不减肥", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 655493}, {"id": 282908, "content": "考上中传MJC，虽然我是三本", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1350695}, {"id": 282910, "content": "啪啪啪啪啪啪啪啪啪", "image": null, "praise_count": 51, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 740032}, {"id": 283166, "content": "一个去旅行", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1351768}, {"id": 282911, "content": "考上985名校 义无反顾的学习", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1286590}, {"id": 283167, "content": "一人去旅行。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1351768}, {"id": 282913, "content": "离婚、争孩子抚养权", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 572478}, {"id": 282914, "content": "这个社会诱惑太多了，一个抖音一个吃鸡就能杀掉所有学习时间！希望能自学几门技术（编程，设计，英语，即使学个占星，占卜也是好的。即使将来不一定用的上。）坚持住，学会和孤独共处，付出全力，戒骄戒躁，踏实一点。不再彷徨迷茫，担忧。", "image": "img/option/option/20180521124558iqZ0S7mF5EreNcou", "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1350055}, {"id": 286242, "content": "去做一个环球旅行者", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1368639}, {"id": 282915, "content": "摘掉虚伪，放下恐惧。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1296632}, {"id": 282916, "content": "改掉自己厌恶的坏习惯", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1273754}, {"id": 285220, "content": "拿下年级第一", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1362453}, {"id": 282917, "content": "从没约过炮，去试一次？", "image": null, "praise_count": 159, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1310496}, {"id": 283173, "content": "十年不交女朋友", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1317336}]}